# Debug / test artifacts — all ad-hoc session screenshots (img*, windows*, etc.)
# stay out, but the theme-gallery and settings-dialog set generated by
# tools/take-screenshots.ps1 / take-settings-screenshots.ps1 IS tracked so
# the README can render them from GitHub.
screenshots/*
!screenshots/theme-*.png
!screenshots/settings-*.png
!screenshots/icon-preview.png
/ghp.txt
